<h2> Notes </h2>

<p>
When @EM{{@HI{{dai}}}} is used with a question, it must be an interrogative one:
<a href="grammar-particle-kai.html">@HI{{kai}}</a> is used with yes-no questions.
</p>

<p>
@EM{{@HI{{dai}}}} is actually the <a href="grammar-copula.html">copula</a> followed by @HI{{i}}, so it can only
follow @HI{{na}}-adjectives and nouns. It can follow @HI{{i}}-adjectives and verbs if the form @EM{{@HI{{ndai}}}}
as the @HI{{nn}} is an abbreviation of the nominaliser <a href="grammar-no-nominaliser.html">@HI{{no}}</a>.
</p>

